      "seed": 1580293355,
      "version": 1000,
      "versionNonce": 1860821530,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773096796933,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "March 6 Agenda:\n- BASIC user functionality (see above)\n- Details:\n  - how should it operate (see RequestBasket)\n  - how should it look (ShadCN default template)\n- how do we implement that functionality?\n  \n  - NO TESTING FOR NOW\n",
      "fontSize": 55.16897397501624,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "March 6 Agenda:\n- BASIC user functionality (see above)\n- Details:\n  - how should it operate (see RequestBasket)\n  - how should it look (ShadCN default template)\n- how do we implement that functionality?\n  \n  - NO TESTING FOR NOW\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1ly2IweB9MoNjY3GDRoju",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 270.14452406158534,
      "y": 915.8995476435716,
      "width": 1559.3501931391966,
      "height": 1034.4182620315546,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6Ip",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1314127174,
      "version": 1545,
      "versionNonce": 969482639,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773175046295,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We need to know the shape of the data so that we can\ncreate mock data to build our Front-end around\n- what are API endpoints? \nGET /bins   (high level info)\nGET /bin/:id  (including all requests)\nPOST /create_bin  (expect bin details in response)\nDELETE /bin_requests/:id\nDELETE /bin/:id\n\n- RESPONSE: \n     - what is shape of data returned from those\nendpoints?  \n     - Need to know immediately so that we can mock w/\njsonserver\n- REQUESTS: can wait on this",
      "fontSize": 55.16897397501624,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We need to know the shape of the data so that we can create mock data to build our Front-end around\n- what are API endpoints? \nGET /bins   (high level info)\nGET /bin/:id  (including all requests)\nPOST /create_bin  (expect bin details in response)\nDELETE /bin_requests/:id\nDELETE /bin/:id\n\n- RESPONSE: \n     - what is shape of data returned from those endpoints?  \n     - Need to know immediately so that we can mock w/ jsonserver\n- REQUESTS: can wait on this",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
