      "updated": 1773096790634,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TECH\n  - Vite  (use template if appropriate)\n  - shadcn\n  - Husky, prettier, ESLint\n  - ReactRouter\n  - TypeScript\n  - Fetch (not Axios)\n  - Zod (if possible)\n  - other tech?\n  - template\n  - file structure\n      - Fullstackopen (Jonathan GDoc)\n      - BulletproofReact",
      "fontSize": 37.41344212098805,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TECH\n  - Vite  (use template if appropriate)\n  - shadcn\n  - Husky, prettier, ESLint\n  - ReactRouter\n  - TypeScript\n  - Fetch (not Axios)\n  - Zod (if possible)\n  - other tech?\n  - template\n  - file structure\n      - Fullstackopen (Jonathan GDoc)\n      - BulletproofReact",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
